OL,3,CUK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds over failed migrant
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FThe UK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,8,Fmillions of pounds over the failed
OL,9,Fmigrant deportation deal after winning
OL,10,Fan international court case.
OL,12,FRwanda sued Britain for more than #100
OL,13,Fmillion, claiming it breached the
OL,14,Fterms of its agreement and is owed
OL,15,Fmoney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780369437
OL,3,CUK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds over failed migrant
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FLawyers representing Britain argued at
OL,8,Fa hearing in March at The Hague's
OL,9,FPermanent Court of Arbitration in the
OL,10,FNetherlands that it was "entirely
OL,11,Flogical" the plan would be scrapped
OL,12,Fwhen Labour came into power after the
OL,13,F2024 general election and that it was
OL,14,F"simple common sense" that no further
OL,15,Fpayments would be due.
OL,17,FAccording to legal documents, Rwanda
OL,18,Fasked the court to find the UK in
OL,19,Fbreach of the agreement and demanded
OL,20,Fpayment of all outstanding sums and
OL,21,Fcompensation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780369437
OL,3,CUK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds over failed migrant
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FBut the UK denied it had breached the
OL,8,Fdeal and said that the east African
OL,9,Fnation "is not entitled to any of the
OL,10,Fforms of relief it seeks" when asking
OL,11,Fthe court to dismiss the claims.
