OL,3,CUK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds over failed migrant
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FEarlier this year, Downing Street
OL,8,Fdefended the decision to scrap the
OL,9,Fscheme, brought forward by the former
OL,10,FConservative government, when it
OL,11,Femerged that Rwanda was taking the UK
OL,12,Fto court.
OL,14,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,15,Fdeclared the plan "dead and buried" as
OL,16,Fone of his first moves in office.
OL,26,@wD@SOUwD@cO]
