OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780369437
OL,3,CUK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds over failed migrant
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FBefore the election, Rishi Sunak's
OL,8,Fgovernment had already spent #700
OL,9,Fmillion on its flagship immigration
OL,10,Fpolicy, where migrants who arrived in
OL,11,Fthe UK by boat from France would be
OL,12,Fsent straight to Rwanda's capital,
OL,13,FKigali, in an attempt to deter Channel
OL,14,Fcrossings.
OL,16,FUltimately, only four volunteers
OL,17,Farrived in Rwanda before the plan was
OL,18,Fscrapped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
