FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780369437
OL,3,CUK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds over failed migrant
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FRwanda's minister of justice and
OL,8,Fattorney general, Emmanuel
OL,9,FUgirashebuja, previously told the
OL,10,Fcourt the country incurred
OL,11,F"significant costs" in preparation for
OL,12,Fthe deal but the UK "then sought to
OL,13,Fwalk away from its legal obligations".
OL,15,FHe also said the UK "did not do Rwanda
OL,16,Fa courtesy of informing it in advance"
OL,17,Fthat it was scrapping the deal, and
OL,18,Fleaders were "left to read about this
OL,19,Fdevelopment in the media".
