OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780369437
OL,3,CUK will not have to pay Rwanda
OL,4,Cmillions of pounds over failed migrant
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FDespite this, in 2024, Rwandan
OL,8,FPresident Paul Kagame suggested
OL,9,FBritish taxpayers' money could be
OL,10,Frepaid if the deal failed.
OL,12,FIn a document setting out Rwanda's
OL,13,Fclaim, Ugirashebuja asked the court to
OL,14,Frule that the UK had breached the
OL,15,Fagreement and should pay about #100
OL,16,Fmillion that it was due to receive in
OL,17,Ftwo instalments in 2024 and 2025, plus
OL,18,F#6 million in compensation and
OL,19,Finterest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
